caption: If you're struggling to follow a diet or to reduce your calorie intake in service of a desire to lose weight, it may mean that there is some work that you need to do before embarking on a weight loss journey that will help you be more successful. Often, we need to allocate time and energy to making adaptive changes so we can be successful with the technical changes. Don't keep shooting yourself in the foot. The One Step approach will help set you up for the long-term success you're looking for.
